{'id': '963579064', 'text': "Thank you for your kind words! We're thrilled you enjoyed the peaceful beachside setting and the quality of our rooms, breakfast, and dinner. We're also glad our team made you feel welcome and well cared for. We look forward to your next stay with us!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team", 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579158', 'text': "Thank you for your fantastic review! We’re thrilled to hear that you felt right at home with us at Roman Beach. It's wonderful to know that our team, including Sugath, Ravindu, and Warna, made such a positive impact on your stay. We’re also glad you enjoyed the meals and the peaceful beach location. We look forward to the opportunity to welcome you back in the future!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team", 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579208', 'text': 'Thank you for your wonderful review! We’re thrilled you enjoyed your stay at Roman Beach Hotel and appreciated our delicious food and the friendly service from Bhagya and Sugar. We’re also pleased to hear that you found the pool, garden, and room to be charming and comfortable. Your recommendation means a lot to us. We hope to welcome you back for another great stay!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579352', 'text': 'Thank you for your amazing review! We’re thrilled to hear that you had a wonderful stay and felt so well taken care of at Roman Beach Hotel. It’s great to know you enjoyed the beautiful location, the cleanliness of the pool area, and the special beach dinner. We’re also pleased to hear that Sugath and our entire team made a positive impact on your stay. Your recommendation means a lot to us. We look forward to welcoming you back!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579394', 'text': 'Thank you for your fantastic review! We’re delighted to hear that everything about your stay at Roman Beach Hotel was perfect. It’s wonderful to know that our staff, including Sugath and our chef, made your experience so special. We’re thrilled you enjoyed the clean rooms, delicious food, and the beautiful beach dinner. Your 10/10 rating and recommendation mean a lot to us. We hope to welcome you back for another memorable stay!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579461', 'text': 'Thank you for your kind review! We’re delighted to hear that you loved our hospitality and enjoyed the attentive service from Silva and the entire team. It’s great to know you appreciated the private beach access and set menus. Your feedback on the bar is noted, and we’ll work on improving it. We look forward to welcoming you back!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579518', 'text': 'Thank you for your heartfelt review! We’re thrilled to hear that you and your family had such a special stay with us at Roman Beach. It’s wonderful to know you enjoyed the quiet location, beautiful decor, and spacious rooms with stunning sea views. We’re especially pleased that our team, including Sugath, Warune, Supan, and the entire staff, made your stay memorable. Your compliments on our food and service mean a lot to us. We can’t wait to welcome you back for another warm and welcoming experience!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579550', 'text': 'Thank you for your wonderful review! We’re delighted to hear that you enjoyed the peaceful stay and perfect location at Roman Beach. It’s great to know you appreciated the spacious rooms with ocean views and our wonderful staff. Your recommendation means a lot to us, and we look forward to welcoming you back in the future!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579581', 'text': 'Thank you for your fantastic review! We’re thrilled to hear that you had an extraordinary stay at Roman Beach Hotel and enjoyed the beautiful sea views, perfect location, and our attentive staff. It’s wonderful to know that Waruna, Sugath, Bhagya, and the entire team made your experience memorable. Your recommendation means a lot to us, and we look forward to welcoming you back for another great stay!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579627', 'text': 'Thank you for your lovely review! We’re delighted to hear that you enjoyed the relaxing atmosphere, spacious rooms, and direct beach access at Roman Beach. It’s great to know that our staff contributed to your pleasant stay. We hope to welcome you back for more relaxation and sunshine in the future!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '963579669', 'text': 'Thank you for your excellent review! We’re thrilled to hear that you had a great stay at Roman Beach Hotel and enjoyed the friendly service, clean and well-furnished room, and delicious Sri Lankan food. It’s wonderful to know that our quiet and cozy location met your expectations. We look forward to welcoming you back on your next visit to Hikkaduwa!

Best regards,
The Roman Beach Team', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-08-06', 'responder': 'Romantha De silva', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '976530997', 'text': "Dear valued guest,

Firstly, we thank you for this amazing review and recommendation. We're glad to hear that you found the ocean views stunning and that our staff provided the support you needed during your stay. It’s wonderful to know you enjoyed the food and that the room was clean and tidy.

Your recommendation means a lot to us, and we can’t wait to welcome you back for another wonderful experience. Thank you for choosing our hotel, and we look forward to seeing you again soon!", 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-10-24', 'responder': 'Iroshan Chanaka Dassanayaka', 'connectionToSubject': 'Owner'}

{'id': '974344904', 'text': "Dear valued guest,

